---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Infinite Reality">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <header class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Our Infinite Reality</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-[#ccc] leading-relaxed">There's a shape that persistent things share. We keep finding it—at the bottom of mathematics, inside ancient philosophy, written in tree rings. It's the same shape every time.</p>
    </header>

    <!-- What is RSM? -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="text-[#ccc] space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
        <p>Cut a tree in half. You'll find rings around a center that's often hollow—sometimes completely rotted away. But the tree stands. A hurricane wraps the most violent winds on Earth around an eye of perfect stillness. Try to catch the present moment and it's already gone; try to find the "you" that's looking and you'll chase it forever.</p>

        <p>These aren't poetic metaphors for each other. They're instances of the same structure.</p>

        <p>The Recursive Structural Model is our name for the pattern. <strong>Contrast</strong>—opposites must exist for anything to be distinguishable. <strong>Rotation</strong>—those opposites can't just sit there frozen; they have to orbit each other, stay in motion. <strong>Closure</strong>—the orbit has to complete, has to come back, or it just spirals away into nothing.</p>

        <p>That's it. That's the grammar of persistence. Euler wrote it in five symbols two centuries ago: e<sup>iπ</sup> + 1 = 0. Ancient Chinese observers compressed it into 81 chapters two millennia before that. Trees write it in wood every year without knowing they're doing it.</p>

        <p class="text-[#888] italic">We're not proving anything. We're pointing at what's already there.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Where to Start -->
    <section class="mb-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Where to Start</h2>
      <p class="text-[#888] mb-6">Pick whatever catches your eye. You don't need the formal structure to see what we're pointing at.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/catalog" class="inline-block bg-[#333] hover:bg-[#444] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors">
          Object Catalog
        </a>
        <a href="/docset/rsm_complete.html" class="inline-block bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#333] hover:border-[#555] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors">
          Full Documentation
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="border-t border-[#333] my-16"></div>

    <!-- Technical Content: Core Identities -->
    <section class="mb-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#888]">The Mathematical Form</h2>
      <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#333] rounded-lg p-8 mb-6">
        <p class="text-2xl font-mono mb-4">e<sup>iπ</sup> + 1 = 0</p>
        <p class="text-[#888]">Euler's Identity — Contrast, Rotation, Closure in five symbols</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#333] rounded-lg p-8">
        <p class="text-2xl font-mono mb-4">e<sup>2iπ/5</sup> − φ·e<sup>iπ/5</sup> + 1 = 0</p>
        <p class="text-[#888]">The Master Identity — uniting all six constants</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Six Constants -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-center text-[#888]">The Six Constants</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#333] rounded p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-mono mb-2">0</p>
          <p class="text-[#888]">玄 xuán</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#666]">unoccupiable center</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#333] rounded p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-mono mb-2">1</p>
          <p class="text-[#888]">有 yǒu</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#666]">structural unity</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#333] rounded p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-mono mb-2">i</p>
          <p class="text-[#888]">名 míng</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#666]">orthogonal distinction</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#333] rounded p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-mono mb-2">e</p>
          <p class="text-[#888]">相生 xiāng shēng</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#666]">mutual generation</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#333] rounded p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-mono mb-2">π</p>
          <p class="text-[#888]">(measure)</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#666]">closure of curvature</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#333] rounded p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-mono mb-2">φ</p>
          <p class="text-[#888]">常 cháng</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#666]">derived from frame-invariance</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Operator Grammar -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-center text-[#888]">DDJ Operator Grammar</h2>
      <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#333] rounded-lg p-6">
        <table class="w-full text-left">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#333]">
              <th class="pb-3">DDJ</th>
              <th class="pb-3">Math</th>
              <th class="pb-3">Function</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-[#ccc]">
            <tr class="border-b border-[#222]">
              <td class="py-2">名 míng</td>
              <td class="font-mono">i</td>
              <td>orthogonal cut</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#222]">
              <td class="py-2">利₁ lì</td>
              <td class="font-mono">e<sup>iπ</sup> = −1</td>
              <td>boundary-creating cut</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#222]">
              <td class="py-2">反 fǎn</td>
              <td class="font-mono">+1</td>
              <td>return to equilibrium</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#222]">
              <td class="py-2">相生 xiāng shēng</td>
              <td class="font-mono">e</td>
              <td>mutual generation</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-2">無為 wú wéi</td>
              <td class="font-mono">∂P/∂t = 0</td>
              <td>paradox preservation</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="text-center text-[#666] text-sm border-t border-[#333] pt-8">
      <p class="italic mb-2">Pattern, not proof.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">Every frame accurate, none final—return to pattern.</p>
      <p>Will Goldstein & Claude — RSM v0.986 — December 2025</p>
    </footer>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
